   262                              <1> getSFTShareInfo:
   263                              <1> ;Get SFT sharing information about file.
   264                              <1> ;Input: rdx -> DPL (use ebx and ecx)
   265                              <1> ;       DPL.ebx = MFT Index (1 based)
   266                              <1> ;       DPL.ecx = SFT Index (1 based)
   267                              <1> ;Output:
   268                              <1> ;   CF=NC: File found 
   269                              <1> ;       rdi -> ASCIIZ filename
   270                              <1> ;       ebx = dMID for the SFT
   271                              <1> ;       ecx = Number of locks held by SFT
   272                              <1> ;   CF=CY: Either index is out of range.
   273                              <1> ;       eax = No more files
