   359                              <1> freeLocks:
   360                              <1> ;Frees all file locks associated to this rdi. 
   361                              <1> ;Input: rdi -> SFT for this file
   362                              <1> ;       edx = Flag for if we should free locks for process
   363                              <1> ;             -1 -> Free for process (on 5D04h calls)
   364                              <1> ;              0 -> Dont bother (otherwise)
   365                              <1> ;Output: All file locks owned by this process are delinked from the 
