   405                              <1> addSFTtoMFT:
   406                              <1> ;Adds an SFT to the MFT chain and finishes filling in it's share fields. 
   407                              <1> ;Checks for sharing conflicts before adding.
   408                              <1> ;Input: rsi -> SFT to add
