   869                              <1> ;redirection, without resorting to using BIOS functions.
   870                              <1> ;We use the PSP as the buffer for the ioReqPkt.
   871                              <1> ;We obviously do no error checking or Int 24 invokation if things
   872                              <1> ; go wrong with this. 
